flowchart LR
  dev[Developer] -->|push| GH[GitHub mono-repo]
  GH -->|trigger| ADO[Azure DevOps CI]
  ADO -->|build and scan| ACRD[(ACR dev)]
  ADO -->|GitOps PR| GHCfg[gitops/envs/dev]
  GHCfg -->|watch| ArgoCD[Argo CD]
  ArgoCD -->|sync| AKS[(AKS cluster)]

  promo[Promotion pipeline] -->|az acr import| ACRS[(ACR stage)]
  promo -->|az acr import| ACRP[(ACR prod)]
  promo -->|PR| GHCfg2[gitops/envs stage/prod]

  ACRD -.->|pull| AKS
  ACRS -.->|pull| AKS
  ACRP -.->|pull| AKS

  AKS -->|metrics| Prom[Prometheus]
  Prom --> Graf[Grafana]
  user[End user] -->|HTTPS| Ingress[NGINX Ingress]
  Ingress --> Frontend[frontend]
